hopobject.body: What do you want to do when you've finished? shop-proactive.com reviews There is no such thing as a no-risk move, particularly when it involves Bynum’s knees and, more importantly, Bynum’s head. The Cavs are not assured that this move will be a success, but in contrast to the Sixers last season, they are assured it will not completely blow up in their faces. As it pertains to Bynum, those odds are probably as good as you’re going to get.
